* In [[the Dalelands]], clovers grew in the [[Daggerdale]] region.
* Clovers grew in the land of [[High Moor]].
* Clovers grew in [[the Vast]].{{Cite polyhedron/119/The Druid Circle of Chauntea|18}}
* In the [[Moonshae Isles]], clovers grew on the island of [[Alaron]].
* Clovers grew in the [[Midwood]]s area of [[Cormanthor]].
* Clover was known by some to grow in great numbers in areas of [[fey]] presence, serving as indication of a [[fey crossroad]] being near.<ref>{{Cite organized play/LFR/Lost Love|28}}
